### Build system

- build config: `docker-bake.hcl` (targets, cache, tags)
- all stages: `meta-secret/Dockerfile` (single multi-stage file)
- **always run builds via `task <target>`, never via `docker buildx bake` directly**
- after updating any `Cargo.toml`, run `task generate-recipe` to update `recipe.json`

### Task commands

| Action | Command |
|---|---|
| Run tests | `task test` |
| Build all images | `task build` |
| Build + push | `task push` |
| Build meta-server | `task meta-server` |
| Build web image | `task web` |
| Export web dist locally | `task web-local` |
| Export wasm pkg locally | `task wasm-local` |
| Update cargo chef recipe | `task generate-recipe` |
| Run web-ui locally | `task web-run` |
| Add shadcn-vue component | `cd meta-secret/web-cli/ui && npx shadcn-vue@latest add <name>` |
